                  ‚ö† Tentativo
                </button>
                <button
                  class="filter-status-btn filter-status-tbd px-3 sm:px-4 py-2 rounded-lg text-xs sm:text-sm font-medium transition-all"
                  data-status="TBD"
                >
                  ? Por Definir
